'''核桃街'''（Walnut Street）位于[[费城|费城]]市中心，东起[[特拉华河|特拉华河]]，向西穿过中区和西区，长5.57英里（8.96公里）<ref name="delorme">DeLorme Street Atlas USA 2007, Toggle Measure Tool. Retrieved 2007-12-20.</ref>。核桃街以北的平行街道为[[栗树街_(费城)|栗树街]]。

核桃街为该市的高级购物区<ref>Harris, Linda JK. [http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-8822498_ITM "Philadelphia Shopping District Gets Messy Makeover."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-8822498_ITM |date=20071226041728 }}, ''[[The_Philadelphia_Inquirer|The Philadelphia Inquirer]]'', July 31, 2002. Accessed December 16, 2007. "Walking down the 1700 block of Walnut Street, a visitor might conclude that the city's premier shopping district has hit on hard times."</ref>，2005年街道的一段以每平方英尺90美元的租金，以及一些“高档餐饮，零售，文化”的机构，被女装日报列为[[北美洲|北美洲]]最昂贵的零售街道名单第12名<ref>Hall, Cecily. [http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-11584976_ITM "THE WWD LIST: STREETS OF CASH; THE MOST EXPENSIVE RETAIL STREETS BY RENT PER SQUARE FOOT IN NORTH AMERICA."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-11584976_ITM |date=20071226034445 }}, ''[[Women's_Wear_Daily|Women's Wear Daily]]'', October 13, 2005. Accessed December 16, 2007. "*12 Walnut Street, Philadelphia Rent per square foot: $90 Walnut Street is home to Rittenhouse Row..."</ref>。2013年的租金已经上升到平均英尺$ 107，比2012年上升了34%，为该国各购物街中最大的增长百分比<ref>{{cite web|last=Van Allen|first=Peter|title=Walnut Street retail is hot, report says|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/philadelphia/news/2013/10/17/walnut-street-retail-is-hot-report-says.html|work=Philadelphia Business Journal|accessdate=15 November 2013|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126004525/https://www.bizjournals.com/philadelphia/news/2013/10/17/walnut-street-retail-is-hot-report-says.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。多数高档时装店位于宽街和第18街之间，靠近[[里滕豪斯广场|里滕豪斯广场]]。

核桃街剧院位于核桃街825号，是英语世界最古老的连续使用的剧院。

沿着核桃街拥有众多的景点和历史遗迹：[[国家独立历史公园|国家独立历史公园]]、社会山、华盛顿广场、华盛顿广场西、圣詹姆斯酒店、费城股票交易所、太阳石油大厦、核桃街1616号大楼、[[里滕豪斯广场|里滕豪斯广场]]、Estey厅、圣三一教堂。 

